{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499820/extras/add_to_wishlist.gif?t=1738687653\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499820/extras/horizontal_line.png?t=1738687653\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Basketball Simulator delivers a true-to-life basketball shooting experience with intuitive controls. Step onto the court, sink impossible shots, and feel the crowd roar as you chase greatness. Will you become the ultimate three-point legend in your city?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499820/extras/0fcb58032d42ee5ca0a084cd403a546a.gif?t=1738687653\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About Basketball Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Basketball Simulator offers a realistic and immersive basketball shooting experience with easy-to-learn mechanics. Step onto the court, line up your shot, and feel the satisfaction of sinking perfect baskets. Whether you're casually practicing or pushing for high scores, every shot counts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499820/extras/a11463ab691e69168ab6176e98fa2011.gif?t=1738687653\" /> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Train like a pro in a solo free-shooting environment, just like practicing alone at the park. Future updates aim to expand the experience with new scenarios, deeper customization, and exciting game modes like CPU matchups, tournaments, and time trials. Are you ready to become a three-point legend?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3499820/page_bg_generated_